  "text": "The first anomaly in the electron neutrino disappearance channel has been reported by the GALLEX and SAGE experiments [CITATION_1] , which observed a deficit of electron neutrinos at distances of order 1 m from the radioactive source. The anomaly has a statistical significance slightly smaller than 3σ, see also the recent analysis [CITATION_2] .",
